      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little DIY! While it shows significant wear and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it's an affordable entry point for anyone looking for a fix-up opportunity. Grab a bargain and bring this car back to life!",
