    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a bit sad to let this absolute gem go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in stunning, showroom-quality shape\u2014I've babied it since day one and kept it tucked away in the garage. It looks and drives like it's brand new, with a spotless interior and a finish that still has that incredible shine. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love and is ready to hit the road without a single worry, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 48500.0,
