    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2018 BMW M2 in showroom condition. This enthusiast-owned vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The Long Beach Blue paint is flawless, protected by a professional ceramic coating that highlights its deep metallic flake. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with zero wear on the leather bolsters and all carbon fiber trim pieces in perfect state. Every service has been performed on schedule at authorized centers, with all documentation provided. With no modifications, no track time, and zero cosmetic imperfections, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade M2. Includes both keys, original window sticker, and a clean title.",
      "price": 47500.0,
